locations: New York City, New York, USA::(2014)
imdb.plot outline: What better place than New York City to tell the tales of 3 young adults who due to forces out of there control are struggling to see the American Dream. When pressed against a wall we see these adults lash out and make and break there own path to success. None of these 3 know of each others existence but there actions will not only connect them together but impact all of there fates. TOM: Although the oldest he is not only the least successful but the most disillusioned of the three. A loner by heart, yet fails to see how many people in his life care about him. STEVE: The most vocal and determined of the three, Steve has worked hard and found quite possibly the article that will jump start his career. His crave for success is what will unravel a chain of mysterious events. AMY: desperate and led to the brink of eviction Amy quickly realizes she needs to break her barriers and find a way to change her surroundings. Under the innocent appearance lies a hungry witty character.
